```
&lt;project&gt;
...
    &lt;repositories&gt;
        &lt;repository&gt;
            &lt;id&gt;private-repo&lt;/id&gt;
            &lt;url&gt;${URL}&lt;/url&gt;
        &lt;/repository&gt;
    &lt;/repositories&gt;
...
&lt;/project&gt;
```

In your GitHub repo you can add a secret `MAVEN_SERVERS`:

```
[{&quot;id&quot;: &quot;private-repo&quot;, &quot;username&quot;: &quot;USERNAME&quot;, &quot;password&quot;: &quot;PASSWORD&quot;}]
