Your solution is not correct, because in your outer loop you are adding the points to `bfList`:
```java
bfList.add(P[i]);
```
before even checking any condition. So, you have to move it to inner loop:
```java
for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) {
    for (int j = i + 1; j &lt; n; j++) {
        double deltam = distance(P[i], P[j]);
        if (deltam &lt; delta1) {
            delta1 = deltam;
            bfList.clear(); // Clear the list and add the new closest points
            bfList.add(P[i]);
            bfList.add(P[j]);
        }
    }
}

